Date: Wed, 22 Apr 2026 15:57:15 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] docs: soften Agents API callouts into collapsible accordions

Replaces large top-of-page <Info> blocks in feature docs with subtle
<Accordion> components placed lower on each page. Collapsed by default
so they don't interrupt reading flow for UI-first users, but remain
discoverable for anyone building automation.

Also:
- Add an Agents API card to extend/introduction.mdx
- Include Agents API in the api-keys.mdx API list
- Add an Agents API entry to the April 2026 release notes

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>
